headline: Wells Fargo upgrades CSX on new intermodal gains
summary: Investing.com -- Wells Fargo upgraded CSX Corp to Overweight from Equal weight given new commercial agreements that are expected to bring more intermodal freight onto the railroad’s network just as industrywide volume growth slows.
